#. <section class="sutta" id="sn30.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn30.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 30"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 30"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn30.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Supaṇṇavagga"
msgstr "1. Phoenixes"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn30.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Dvayakārīsutta"
msgstr "3. Both Kinds of Deeds"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn30.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.2"
msgid ""
"Aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and "
"said to him:"

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ supaṇṇānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body "
"breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the egg-born phoenixes?”"

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kāyena dvayakārī hoti, vācāya dvayakārī, manasā "
"dvayakārī."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, it’s when someone does both kinds of deeds by body, speech, and "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.5"
msgid "Tassa sutaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "And they’ve heard:"

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.6"
msgid "‘aṇḍajā supaṇṇā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti."
msgstr "‘The egg-born phoenixes are long-lived, beautiful, and very happy.’"

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.7"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ supaṇṇānaṃ sahabyataṃ "
"upapajjeyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the "
"company of the egg-born phoenixes!’"

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.9"
msgid ""
"So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ supaṇṇānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the "
"egg-born phoenixes."

msgctxt "sn30.3:1.10"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ supaṇṇānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why someone, when their body breaks "
"up, after death, is reborn in the company of the egg-born phoenixes.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn30.3:1.11"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
